&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BS/MS in Computer Science, Computer Engineering, a related field, or equivalent practical experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of software engineering experience in production environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with Python and/or Go&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with datastores such as Dynamo DB and cloud-based environments such as AWS&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong proficiency in object-oriented programming and foundational CS concepts (data structures, algorithms)&lt;/li&gt;
